## 3. Data & State Management

### `src/context/SanityContext.tsx`
Fetches all Sanity documents concurrently on mount using `Promise.all` and provides them to the app. 
- Queries: `fetchSiteSettings`, `fetchHero`, `fetchAbout`, `fetchAchievements`, `fetchProjects`, `fetchPhotos`, `fetchExperience`, `fetchPhilosophy`, `fetchQuotes`, `fetchDevMode`.

### `src/context/AchievementContext.tsx`
A global state manager for the hidden Easter egg system.
- Persists unlocked achievements in `localStorage`.
- **7 Hidden Achievements**: `Explorer` (scroll all), `Photographer` (open 5 photos), `Builder` (explore projects), `Curious Mind` (open DevMode), `Architect` (explore DevMode architecture), `Problem Solver` (run 'challenge' command), `Deep Reader` (read a photo story).

